00:02:11.830 --> 00:02:14.740
You were at National Geo
for what, four, five years?

00:02:14.740 --> 00:02:16.040
&gt;&gt; Candice Millard: Six years.

00:02:16.040 --> 00:02:17.340
&gt;&gt; Jonathan Yardley: Six years.

00:02:17.340 --> 00:02:19.230
National Geo has a reputation
