00:05:51.740 --> 00:05:53.800
&gt;&gt; Candice Millard:
Well, I had an advance.

00:05:53.800 --> 00:05:55.100
&gt;&gt; Jonathan Yardley: You did.

00:05:55.100 --> 00:05:56.400
&gt;&gt; Candice Millard: Yeah.

