00:08:29.830 --> 00:08:32.650
&gt;&gt; Jonathan Yardley:
And quite specifically,

00:08:32.650 --> 00:08:36.630
what drew you to Winston Churchill
and his role in the Boer War?

00:08:36.630 --> 00:08:40.790
&gt;&gt; Candice Millard: So I had
heard the story 25 years ago.

00:08:40.790 --> 00:08:43.770
My husband was a journalist for
the New York Times for years

00:08:43.770 --> 00:08:47.840
