Congress in the early '80s.

00:08:51.720 --> 00:08:55.660
And when I met him 25 years ago,
he mentioned to me, he said,

00:08:55.660 --> 00:09:00.280
"Did you know that Winston
Churchill was a prisoner of war

00:09:00.280 --> 00:09:03.020
in South Africa and
that he escaped?"

00:09:03.020 --> 00:09:05.780
And I thought, "You are kidding me.

00:09:05.780 --> 00:09:07.140
How do I not know this?"

00:09:07.140 --> 00:09:11.140
And so it just stayed with
me all of these years.

00:09:11.140 --> 00:09:15.670 position:56%
And after I turned in the manuscript
for my second book, we went to lunch

00:09:15.670 --> 00:09:18.340
