ideas for your next book?"

00:09:18.340 --> 00:09:20.830
And I said, "You know,
I would love to write

00:09:20.830 --> 00:09:23.210
about Winston Churchill
and the Boer War."

00:09:23.210 --> 00:09:25.930
And he said, yes.

00:09:25.930 --> 00:09:28.410
And so, it just went from there.

00:09:28.410 --> 00:09:32.110
&gt;&gt; Jonathan Yardley: I wondered
