00:19:48.490 --> 00:19:49.870
She was this beautiful young woman.

00:19:49.870 --> 00:19:52.550
He had met her actually in India

00:19:52.550 --> 00:19:56.060
when he was there fighting
and British India.

00:19:56.060 --> 00:19:59.560
And she was sort of the toast
of London when she went back.

00:19:59.560 --> 00:20:01.290
And so she had many admirers.

00:20:01.290 --> 00:20:04.250
But he was in love with her
and he wanted to marry her

00:20:04.250 --> 00:20:08.700
but her father wouldn't let her
marry him because he didn't think

00:20:08.700 --> 00:20:11.110
that Churchill would
amount to anything.

00:20:11.110 --> 00:20:13.210
[ Laughter ]

00:20:13.210 --> 00:20:15.520
&gt;&gt; Jonathan Yardley: Finally,
Candice, before we turn this

00:20:15.520 --> 00:20:17.540
