Journal last week describes you

00:20:29.160 --> 00:20:31.760
as "a smooth riding
popular historian".

00:20:31.760 --> 00:20:33.230
I guess that was a compliment.

00:20:33.230 --> 00:20:37.860
But the phrase "popular
history" has always seemed to me

00:20:37.860 --> 00:20:41.400
to be slightly pejorative and
condescending, even though much

00:20:41.400 --> 00:20:43.820
of the best history now being
