00:22:24.710 --> 00:22:26.010
Yeah.

00:22:26.010 --> 00:22:27.310
&gt;&gt; Candice Millard:
Tell stories, right.

00:22:27.310 --> 00:22:28.610
And that's what I love to do.

00:22:28.610 --> 00:22:29.910
Yeah. I agree.

