&gt;&gt; Candice Millard: Yeah.

00:22:42.470 --> 00:22:43.770
Hi.

00:22:43.770 --> 00:22:45.700
&gt;&gt; Well, being a-- part of the
time at least I teach history

00:22:45.700 --> 00:22:47.430
